data.description: Just a Little Ray of Sunshine!        Nestled in the heart of an established neighborhood, this adorable 2-bedroom, 2-bath bungalow with additional office space and a separate outside laundry building is a true gem. Light-filled and exuding happiness at every corner, this home is sweet as can be.     Warm and inviting living space, where natural light dances through the windows, creating an ambiance of pure joy.     The kitchen was recently updated and features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and artsy backsplash.     The primary bedroom offers a private bathroom for your comfort and convenience. Step out onto your large deck, an ideal space for al fresco dining, sipping morning coffee, or simply soaking up the sun. An outbuilding overlooking the creek is a versatile space that can serve as a laundry room and even has space for your personal office or art studio. Imagine working with the tranquil sound of the creek as your backdrop. Don't miss your chance to make this delightful bungalow yours.
